tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE voice_interaction_data (
    interaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    transcript TEXT,
    audio_file BYTEA
);

CREATE TABLE VoiceCommands (
    command_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_id INT,
    command TEXT,
    response TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (interaction_id) REFERENCES VoiceInteractions(interaction_id)
);

CREATE TABLE voice_interactions (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    voice_input TEXT,
    voice_output TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interaction_logs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_id UUID,
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action TEXT
);
